---
// Contact component - Social-First approach (no traditional form)
// Based on expert research 2025: Multi-channel, zero friction, mobile-native
// Sources: YouCanBookMe, TheSalonBusiness, Inference Beauty
// Philosophy: Clients want to book fast, not fill forms (81% abandon forms)
---

